Package voicesplitting.voice

Provides functionality for performing voice separation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Voice
    A Voice is a node in the LinkedList representing a voice.
    VoiceSplittingModel
    A VoiceSplittingModel is an abstract class representing any MidiModel which is used to split MIDI data into voices.
    VoiceSplittingModelState
    A VoiceSplittingModelState is an abstract MidiModelState which splits incoming MidiNotes into Voices.

Package voicesplitting.voice Description

Provides functionality for performing voice separation.

Those wanting to create their own voice splitters should extend the abstract VoiceSplittingModel and VoiceSplittingModelState classes here in a new package, as was done by HmmVoiceSplittingModel and HmmVoiceSplittingModelState.
